  "text": "Therefore, this exercise may be especially useful in elderly individuals with a lower position of the hyoid bone at rest [CITATION_1] and those with decreased elevation of the hyoid bone during swallowing. [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] It is known that both these factors are associated with an increased risk of aspiration.",
